## Development Commands

```bash
# DDEV commands
ddev start              # Start environment
ddev wp [command]       # Run WP-CLI
ddev composer [command] # Run Composer

# Theme development (in theme directory)
ddev npm run dev        # Development
ddev npm run build      # Production build
```

### Common Tasks
```bash
# Clear caches
ddev wp cache flush
ddev wp acorn view:clear

# Database
ddev wp db export backup.sql
ddev wp db import backup.sql
```

